给人嚼舌根?

349
00:24:50,491 --> 00:24:53,118
Do you know what I findworse than being talked about?
你知道我发现比被人嚼舌根更可怕的是什么?

350
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:56,747
Not being talked about at all.
根本不被人谈起

351
00:25:39,915 --> 00:25:41,834
Mrs Erlynne will see you upstairs.
Erlynne太太在楼上见你

352
00:25:46,713 --> 00:25:48,465
