这很贵

356
00:26:08,819 --> 00:26:11,280
- Nothing but the best for you.- I know, I paid for it.
- 只给你最好的- 我知道，是我付的钱

357
00:26:11,738 --> 00:26:13,615
Well, there is that.
都在那了

358
00:26:14,116 --> 00:26:16,243
Should we be drinking thisearly in the day?
我们该这么早就喝酒吗?

359
00:26:16,869 --> 00:26:19,037
Well, somewhere in the worldit's very late.
世界上的某地现在很晚了

360
00:26:19,329 --> 00:26:21,456
I don't want you thinkingI make a habit of this.
我不想让你觉得这样成习惯了

361
00:26:21,999 --> 00:26:23,584
Is that why you look so guilty?
那是你看上去内疚的原因吗?

362
00:26:23,959 --> 00:26:25,627
I don't like lying to her.
我不喜欢跟她说谎

363
00:26:26,211 --> 00:26:28,297
I should go.She's only gone to lunch.
我得走了，她只是去吃饭

364
00:26:31,300 --> 00:26:33,844
This is all the cashI have right now.
这是我现在所有的现金

365
00:26:34,219 --> 00:26:36,471
I'll set you up with an account.
我会给你建个账号

366
00:26:37,264 --> 00:26:39,016
You can draw on it directly.
你就可以直接提取了

367
00:26:39,349 --> 00:26:41,143
I met Meg.
我遇到Meg了

368
00:26:41,810 --> 00:26:43,812
It was by chance.
是个巧遇

369
00:26:44,646 --> 00:26:47,274
