没事的，她不知道我是谁

370
00:26:47,566 --> 00:26:49,067
You spoke to her?
你跟她说话了吗?

371
00:26:49,610 --> 00:26:51,778
Yes, for a minute.She's very pretty.
对，很短，她很漂亮

372
00:26:53,405 --> 00:26:57,034
How did you two meet?Was it love at first sight?
你们俩怎么遇上的?是一见钟情吗?

373
00:26:57,910 --> 00:26:59,620
I have to go.
我得走了

374
00:26:59,828 --> 00:27:01,663
I'm curious. It's only natural.
我好奇，很自然的

375
00:27:01,872 --> 00:27:03,999
There's no pointto these questions.
这些问题没意义

376
00:27:05,584 --> 00:27:07,836
- Do you love her?- Very much.
- 你爱她吗?- 很爱

377
00:27:09,338 --> 00:27:11,548
I'd rather cut off my armthan see Meg hurt.
我宁可断臂也不想让Meg受伤

378
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:14,134
Are you protecting her oryour reputation?
你是在保护她还是保护你的名声?

379
00:27:14,426 --> 00:27:16,803
You don't know me at all.
你对我一无所知

380
00:27:21,058 --> 00:27:22,809
Did he work on yourwedding night?
他在你们的新婚之夜也工作吗?

381
00:27:26,647 --> 00:27:29,483
He's very conscientiousand I respect him for it.
他很尽责，我为此而敬重他

382
00:27:29,816 --> 00:27:32,027
Suppose it wasn't work,suppose he had a mistress.
假设不是因为工作，假设他有情妇

383
00:27:33,195 --> 00:27:35,072
