不，那岂不让她跟那丈夫一样坏了吗?

387
00:27:41,411 --> 00:27:43,205
Modern marriage thrives onmutual deception.
现代婚姻因彼此欺骗而兴旺

388
00:27:43,413 --> 00:27:45,499
We are completely honestwith each other.
我们彼此完全忠诚

389
00:27:45,624 --> 00:27:47,417
You should makehim your model.
你该以他为榜样

390
00:27:47,751 --> 00:27:50,796
I intend to.From this moment on.
我正打算，从现在开始

391
00:27:52,172 --> 00:27:53,924
Don't you like it?
你不喜欢吗?

392
00:27:55,801 --> 00:27:58,053
Oh, I'm saving it for Robert.He loves figs.
哦，我给Robert留着，他喜欢无花果

393
00:27:58,929 --> 00:28:00,722
Share mine, then.
那吃我的吧

394
00:28:03,433 --> 00:28:05,102
Can we go to thetelegraph office?
我们能去电报局吗?

395
00:28:06,144 --> 00:28:08,021
He probably hasn't eaten.
他可能还没吃东西呢

396
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:15,362
Alberto? Fabrizio?
Alberto? Fabrizio?

397
00:28:16,363 --> 00:28:17,906
Oh, what's his name?
哦，他叫什么?

398
00:28:18,365 --> 00:28:19,741
Mario?
Mario?

399
00:28:20,409 --> 00:28:21,910
Barman.
酒保

400
00:28:22,286 --> 00:28:23,871
Whisky.
威士忌

401
00:28:24,663 --> 00:28:27,666
And another thing, your Mrs Erlynnehas no principles at all.
另外, 你的Erlynne太太完全没有原则

402
00:28:28,125 --> 00:28:29,877
I like people more than principles.
我喜欢人甚于原则

403
00:28:30,210 --> 00:28:32,838
And people without principles,even better.
没原则的人就更好了

404
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:36,425
But Lord Augustus, she onlywants you for your money.
但是Augustus大人她只是要你的钱啊

405
00:28:36,633 --> 00:28:38,594
Now why shouldn't she?It's my best asset.
她干嘛不能？那是我最好的资产

406
00:28:39,219 --> 00:28:42,181
Old-ish, fat-ish,absolutely no brain...
又老又胖，完全无脑

407
00:28:42,431 --> 00:28:43,891
heaps and heaps of banknotes.
成堆的钞票

408
00:28:44,183 --> 00:28:45,934
