并不需要贬低自己，Tuppy

409
00:28:45,934 --> 00:28:47,394
Your friends can always do that.
让你的朋友们来嘛

410
00:28:50,314 --> 00:28:54,526
Down by the marina, strolling along,pretty as you please...
在码头，一起徘徊，跟你一样美……

411
00:28:54,568 --> 00:28:57,654
guess who I saw withLord Darlington?
猜我看见谁跟Darlington大人在一起?

412
00:29:05,162 --> 00:29:06,788
They haven't seen him today.
他们今天没看见他

413
00:29:29,186 --> 00:29:31,104
Do you know wheremy husband is?
你知道我丈夫在哪吗?

414
00:29:31,396 --> 00:29:33,732
I thought he leftafter you, signora.
我以为他跟你一起走了，女士

415
00:29:37,486 --> 00:29:38,779
Robert?
Robert?

416
00:30:01,301 --> 00:30:03,011
How was lunch?
午饭怎样?

417
00:30:03,345 --> 00:30:05,597
We went to the telegraph office.Where were you?
我们去电报局了，你去哪了?

418
00:30:06,557 --> 00:30:09,059
Well, we must have justmissed each other.
我们也许刚巧错过了

419
00:30:42,134 --> 00:30:45,721
Now I see uncle.He's with the american woman.
现在我看见叔叔了他跟那美国女人在一起

420
00:30:47,973 --> 00:30:50,350
Too much rouge and notenough clothing.
口红过多，衣服过少

421
00:30:50,684 --> 00:30:52,895
