那是女人的拿手好戏

423
00:30:55,063 --> 00:30:58,400
I heard she left New Yorkwithout paying her hotel bill.
我听说她离开New York连酒店的帐都没付

424
00:30:58,609 --> 00:31:00,319
Quite a scandal.
真是个丑闻

425
00:31:00,527 --> 00:31:03,238
- Who? Someone you know?- Someone you don't want to know.
- 谁? 你认识的人吗?- 是个你不想认识的人

426
00:31:03,906 --> 00:31:05,741
No. Steer clear.
不，Steer Clear

427
00:31:05,991 --> 00:31:07,951
She's the onewith Lord Augustus.
她就是跟Augustus大人在一起的

428
00:31:08,452 --> 00:31:10,162
You've met Mrs Erlynne,haven't you?
你已经认识Erlynne太太了，是吧？

429
00:31:10,621 --> 00:31:13,415
- No.- But I've seen you.
- 没有.- 可我看见你了

430
00:31:13,874 --> 00:31:16,752
Oh, was that your foot?
哦，那是你的脚吗?

431
00:31:17,669 --> 00:31:19,838
Wherever do you findshoes to fit?
你到哪去找合脚的鞋啊?

432
00:31:20,172 --> 00:31:22,382
