Erlynne, 对了，她有了一些进项

443
00:31:54,998 --> 00:31:58,293
- I made an investment for her.- An inheritance, I suppose?
- 我为她管理投资- 是遗产吧，我猜?

444
00:31:59,837 --> 00:32:02,339
The woman in the shop.I told you, remember?
商店里的女人，我告诉过你的，记得吗?

445
00:32:02,673 --> 00:32:03,924
The dress?
套装?

446
00:32:04,591 --> 00:32:07,302
No, back and almost no front.You could see everything.
不，后背，几乎没有前片你什么都能看见

447
00:32:07,511 --> 00:32:08,804
