很不像样

448
00:32:09,137 --> 00:32:10,889
You're just not used toItalian fashions, that's all.
你只是不习惯意大利时装而已

449
00:32:11,139 --> 00:32:12,850
No, I'm sure your wife ison the mark.
我觉得你妻子挺合拍的

450
00:32:13,433 --> 00:32:15,686
Mrs Erlynne is anotorious Jezebel.
Erlynne太太是个声名狼藉的无耻女人

451
00:32:16,103 --> 00:32:18,564
That's a slanderous statement. If youcan't back it up, I wouldn't repeat it.
那是诽谤，如果你不收回，我不会重复

452
00:32:19,606 --> 00:32:22,109
