好

489
00:34:07,923 --> 00:34:11,510
I can't believe it - she's got him!
我不敢相信，她钓上他了

490
00:34:13,136 --> 00:34:14,847
Poor Tuppy.
可怜的Tuppy

491
00:34:27,276 --> 00:34:29,027
