你不得不逃走

573
00:39:57,814 --> 00:39:59,983
You can't think of anything else.
你什么事都无法想

574
00:40:00,526 --> 00:40:02,069
Or anyone else.
什么人都无法想

575
00:40:03,570 --> 00:40:05,572
You married the wrong man,that's all.
你只是嫁错了人

576
00:40:09,451 --> 00:40:11,370
He married the wrong woman.
他娶错了人

577
00:40:13,539 --> 00:40:14,957
