很晚了

578
00:40:15,958 --> 00:40:17,584
It's time for bed.
该上床了

579
00:40:18,335 --> 00:40:19,628
Sleep.
睡觉

580
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,672
"...Perchance to dream".
"偶然的梦境"

581
00:40:22,047 --> 00:40:24,299
That's the bard, you know.I'm a bit of a reader myself.
是吟游诗人，你知道我自己也读过点书的

582
00:40:24,508 --> 00:40:26,593
So you said. Goodnight, Tuppy.
照你说的，晚安，Tuppy

583
00:40:30,681 --> 00:40:32,641
I hate the taste of tobacco.
我讨厌烟草味

584
00:40:37,187 --> 00:40:38,689
Well - that's it then.
好，就这样

585
00:40:45,821 --> 00:40:48,699
I quit. On the spot.
我戒了，当场

586
00:40:52,077 --> 00:40:54,079
What else can I tell you?
我还能告诉你什么?

587
00:40:56,081 --> 00:40:58,000
I'm a very rich man, you know.
我是个非常富有的人，你知道

588
00:40:59,251 --> 00:41:01,128
You're a very nice man.
你是个非常好的人

589
00:41:01,962 --> 00:41:03,255
Go to bed.
上床吧

590
00:41:08,468 --> 00:41:10,554
You know, I'm glad I quit.
你知道，我很高兴戒烟了

591
00:41:12,764 --> 00:41:14,433
