00:42:31,134 --> 00:42:32,427
it wouldn't look right.
但看上去不对

605
00:42:32,636 --> 00:42:34,429
Gold looks right with everything.Just wear it. No-one has to know.
金子衬什么都行，戴上就是了不需要人知道

606
00:42:34,596 --> 00:42:37,140
