00:43:06,837 --> 00:43:09,423
Signora, the florist is waitingfor his money.
女主人，花匠在等着拿工钱

617
00:43:09,673 --> 00:43:11,258
I'll have to get it fromMr Windemere.
我得跟Windemere先生拿

618
00:43:11,425 --> 00:43:12,885
Can he come back later?
他能呆会儿再来吗?

619
00:43:13,093 --> 00:43:14,887
Has Robert a cheque-bookin his office?
Robert 在办公室不是有支票本吗？

620
00:43:15,053 --> 00:43:16,930
